Contact Us & FAQ’s
We’d Love to Hear From You!
Questions? Let us help! Reach out and start your Daytona RV adventure today!
For more information please call us at
(386)-257-6137
or email us at
daytonarvoasis@gmail.com
FAQ
‘s
Q.  What time is check in and check out?
A. Check in is anytime after 12:00 pm and Check out is 11:00 am
Q.  How far from I-95 are you?
A.  Just 1/4 mile.  Late Check In available.
Q.  How far are you from the Speedway?
A. 1.5 miles
Q.  How far is the Beach
?
A.  6 miles
Q.  Do you have nearby shopping?
A. Yes, Volusia Mall and Tanger Outlet Mall are within a 5 minute drive and Daytona Flea Market is right across the street!  We even have our own entrance.
Q.  Are your sites full hookup?
A. Yes, all of our sites have water, electric (30 & 50 amp), and sewer.  And we have several large Deluxe Pull Thru sites to accommodate the biggest rigs.
Q.  Do you have WIFI?
A.  Yes, but it is not meant for streaming.
Q.  Are you pet friendly?
A. Yes, with certain breed restrictions. Please call us at 386-257-6137. All pets must kept on a leash in hand at all times and cleaned up after.
Q.  Do you have shuttle service during the Races and the Concert?
A. Yes, there is shuttle service available ($).
